'agpeya.come_let_us_worship.title': 'O, come, let us worship',
'agpeya.come_let_us_worship.text': 'O’ Come, let us worship; <br>O’ Come, let us ask Christ our God. <br>O’ Come, let us worship; <br>O’ Come, let us ask Christ our King. <br>O’ Come, let us worship; <br>O’ Come, let us implore Christ our Saviour. <br>Our Lord Jesus Christ, the word of God, keep us through the intercessions of St Mary and all your Saints, and let us enjoy a fresh start. Have mercy upon us according to Your will forever. The night had passed away, we thank You, O’ Lord, and ask You to keep us this day without sin and deliver us.',
