'agpeya.psalm_146.text': 'Hallelujah! Bless the Lord, O my soul! <br> I will praise the Lord all my life, do not want to play my God as long as I am. <br> Trust in Noble, a son of man, in which no help! <br> His spirit goes out, he returns to his earth. on the same day his plans go lost <br> Happy is he whose help is the God of Jacob, whose hope is in the Lord his God stands, download heaven and earth has made the sea and all that is in them; who keeps faith forever. <br> He makes right the oppressed, he gives bread to the hungry. The Lord makes the prisoners free. <br> the Lord opens the eyes of the blind. The Lord directed to the humble. . The Lord loves the righteous <br> The LORD preserves the strangers, orphans and widows, he helps on; but he bends the way of the wicked. <br> The Lord will reign forever, your God, O Zion, from generation to generation. <B> Hallelujah! </ B>',
